headline: BALL to Boost Presence With Stake in Benepack's European Can Business
summary: Ball Corp moves to expand its European reach with an 80% stake in Benepack's can operations, strengthening its sustainable packaging network.

headline: Ball buys majority stake in Benepack’s European beverage can unit
summary: The deal covers two production facilities, one in Belgium and one in Hungary.
